These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, hedgehog
There are 2 different favourite colors: purple, blood-red
There 2 different types of food: watermelon, tomato
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, marigold
1. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
2. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
3. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Pet      | hedgehog      | goldfish    |
| Color           | blood-red | purple |
| Food   | watermelon       | tomato  |
| Flower     | bellflower      | marigold     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
2 different games are played: domino, scrabble
City: hannover, paris
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: tulip, daisy
There are 2 different favourite colors: azure, chestnut
1. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the person who likes chestnut##3
2. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
3. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Game          | scrabble | domino |
| City   | hannover       | paris         |
| Flower           | daisy     | tulip         |
| Color     | chestnut    | azure    |

