.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, balloon-flower
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, mexican
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, surfing
1. the mexican is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate          | mirinda |
| Flower           | balloon-flower | daffodil     |
| Nationality   | chinese            | mexican         |
| Sport     | surfing         | rugby   |

