.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-4::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: pink, blood-red
House: palace, gothic-revival
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, march
There are 2 different nationalities: turkish, canadian
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the canadian##3
2. the person who likes blood-red is the turkish##1
3. the person who likes pink is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Color      | blood-red     | pink   |
| House   | gothic-revival    | palace |
| Birthday   | may   | march |
| Nationality           | turkish | canadian    |

