.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  freelancer, entrepreneur
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, march
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, rowing
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, photography
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the freelancer##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Job      | entrepreneur     | freelancer |
| Birthday          | march   | may |
| Sport   | rowing     | rugby     |
| Hobby     | magic-tricks | photography     |

 